  "text": "The on-demand flexibility and mobility of the UAVs come at the price of SWaP limitations. To manage these limitations, resource allocation techniques specifically for UAVs have been studied [CITATION_1] - [CITATION_2] . It is important to make sure that the optimal resource allocation would not sacrifice other performance metrics such as transmission rate, spectrum, optimal UAV's placement, user QoS, etc. However, as all the existing works mention that there is not enough research work covering all aspects of the resource allocation of UAV-based networks.",
  "correct_citation": {
